comment: The set of multiples of _m_, mℤ, is a subset of those of _n_, nℤ, iff _n_ divides _m_. Lemma 2.1(a) of ~ https://www.mscs.dal.ca/~~selinger/3343/handouts/ideals.pdf p. 5, with mℤ and nℤ as images of the divides relation under _m_ and _n_. (Contributed by Steve Rodriguez, 20-Jan-2020.)
